Sensor and (433 MHz) RF, Heatpump (IR) Control Box
==================================================

ESP01 and Arduino Pro Mini

How to use
----------
- In esp/, copy include/settings.h.template to include/settings.h
- Adjust settings as required (Wifi credentials, MQTT server, MQTT topics)
- Compile with pio run, upload with pio run -t upload
- In atmega/, compile with pio run and upload with pio -t upload
- If HeatpumpIR library doesn't compile, remove dependency IRSenderESP8266 from library.json
